        <title>Rocketlab 电子号 The Mountain God Guards任务,全球年度第128次轨道发射</title>
        <link>https://ai.programnotes.cn/p/rocketlab-%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%B7-the-mountain-god-guards%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E7%AC%AC128%E6%AC%A1%E8%BD%A8%E9%81%93%E5%8F%91%E5%B0%84/</link>
